<h1>Newbie Help Pages</h1>

<p><strong>newbie</strong> (noun) When you say someone is a 
<strong>newbie</strong>, you mean they are new to a group 
or an activity. <em>Dawgspeak's mission statement is to show 
<strong>newbies</strong> how to speak with slang. </em></p>
<p>We have specialized pages to assist us in this mission, 
each one tailor-made to guide the uninitiated through a specific 
topic. Click any of the following to begin your education 
on all the subjects anyone needs to know to survive in Athens:</p>
</div>
</div>

